class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70849882bdb25552bb7d8783099755153effb6ff","tid":1553642,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0f16c92a5fcdaf4f9a8600fc6f8f170e78b152a","tid":1553642,"uid":94441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"推 聽日美國國會復會"},{"pid":"f9acc154edcffb1409c0b899b8dafb7545120195","tid":1553642,"uid":59554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7052054bc9c8686a53f5ea7bd3177b77f164b4b","tid":1553642,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"真係有美國嘅清朝鐵路債券持有人走去告中共。Russell Jackson 同另外嘅湖廣鐵路債券持有人入稟阿拉巴馬洲嘅法院。當時北京用有用國際法嘅sovereignty immunity，甚至就呢件件事出過外交照會，但可唔可以將豁免權嘅適用範圍擴展到商業活動都係爭議點之一。<br />\n(判辭全文: <a href=\"https://law.justia.com/cases/federal/district-courts/FSupp/550/869/1451489/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaw.justia.com%2Fcases%2Ffederal%2Fdistrict-courts%2FFSupp%2F550%2F869%2F1451489%2F&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=519a9323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://law.justia.com/cases/federal/district-courts/FSupp/550/869/1451489/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n當時判辭寫點解可以搵中共攞錢嘅原因同背景係:<br />\n<br />\nIt is an established principle of international law that &quot;[c]hanges in the government or the internal policy of a state do not as a rule affect its position in international law. A monarchy may be transformed into a republic, or a republic into a monarchy; absolute principles may be substituted for constitutional, or the reverse; but, though the government changes, the nation remains, with rights and obligations unimpaired.&quot; Lehigh Valley R. Co. v. State of Russia, 21 F.2d 396, 401 (2d Cir. 1927) (quoting Moore, Digest International Law, vol. 1, p. 249). The People's Republic of China is the successor government to the Imperial Chinese Government and, therefore, the successor to its obligations. The People's Republic of China has made no provision for payment of the principal due on the Hukuang bonds.<br />\n<br />\n而最後嘅裁決竟然係:<br />\n<br />\nDefendant, The People's Republic of China, has defaulted in this action. Its default was entered on October 22, 1981. The issue of the amount of damages sustained by the plaintiff class was submitted to the Court and the Court determined that plaintiffs suffered damages in the amount of Forty-One Million, Three-Hundred Thirteen Thousand, Thirty-Eight Dollars and 00/100 Cents ($41,313,038.00).<br />\n<br />\nPursuant to and in accordance with the Memorandum Opinion entered contemporaneously herewith, it is, therefore,<br />\nORDERED, ADJUDGED and DECREED that plaintiffs recover the sum of $41,313,038.00 with interest thereon at the legal rate from and after the 1st day of September, 1982, together with costs of this action.<br />\n<br />\n換言之，係影響到南京條約同北京條約前，中國都要處理埋以往起鐵路嘅債。再俾嘅話中國應該真係冇錢。<br />\n<br />\n同時，如果唔俾即係承認自己不是大清同國民政府嘅繼承人，而香港就&hellip;&hellip;屬於邊個都唔知，因為中共唔打算繼承大清政府嘅嘢。噤嘅話南京條約、北京條約、展拓新界界址專條同中英聯合聲明，以至香港回歸呢個事實都會俾「改寫」。因為香港主權不屬於中共而屬於國民政府、大清政府同英國，噤香港根本唔需要回歸。<br />\n<br />\n要求中國還清朝政府國債, 唔還就放棄香港統治, 入黎簽左佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcwjoPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcwjoPE.jpg&h=13992bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=943f6fc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n大家幫手簽左佢啦<br />\n要中国還錢, 唔還錢就放棄香港統治"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"個聯署好似又壞左"},{"pid":"7f6108a3f16e78dc1475b9021b954a8733a0bbf2","tid":1553642,"uid":67632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"